org.matsim.contrib.socnetgen.sna.graph.spatial.io

Class SpatialGraphKMLWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.contrib.socnetgen.sna.graph.spatial.io.SpatialGraphKMLWriter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    KMLVertexPropertyWriter

    public class SpatialGraphKMLWriter
extends Object
    A class to encode spatial graphs into a KML format. The encode graph will be packed with additional resources into a KMZ file.
    Author:
    jillenberger

      • setKmlPartitition

        public void setKmlPartitition(KMLPartitions kmlPartitition)
        Sets the KMLPartitions object to use with this writer. The writer will create one folder for each partition in the main KML document. The default KMLPartitions object returns the whole graph as one partition.
        Parameters:
        kmlPartitition - a KMLParatitions object
